<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA38">
<l>īṇṭoḷicēr vāṉat teḻumatiyai vāḷaravan</l>
<l>tīṇṭac ciṟukiyatē pōlātē - pūṇṭatōr</l>
<l>tārēṟu pāmpuṭaiyāṉ mārpi ṟaḻaintilaṅku</l>
<l>kūrēṟu kārēṉak kompu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While the moon rising here in the luminous sky is gripped by the bright snake,</l>
<l>it does not seem to diminish, the tusk of the black boar that rises sharply,</l>
<l>thriving [and] shining on the chest of him who possesses a snake</l>
<l>that rises as the garland that he wears.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
